


 	 Orbystopia is a text based game, you can enter the following commands to control your character.
	  
	 each command will ask you to enter further information but you can also combine your answer in one command, 

	 for example float forward instead of float and then forward.


			float [direction] ---> forward, left, up, down etc. to move around.
			show [stats/directions] ---> to show character stats or directions.
			search [cell/terminal] ---> to search cell or terminal.
			use ---> to use item by entering it's id.
			link ---> to jack in to cyberspace(when asked enter yes to jack in or anything else to continue).
			quit ---> to quit game.
			help ---> to display this page.
